---
import ArticleLayout from '../../layouts/ArticleLayout.astro';

const locale = 'en';
---

<!-- [Customize this page for your site] -->
<ArticleLayout
  title="About"
  description="Learn what this static tool site starter provides and how its browser-based tools work."
  locale={locale}
  updated="2026-06-28"
>
  <p>
    This site is a reusable starter for fast, static, browser-based tools. It is
    designed for small utilities that help visitors complete practical tasks
    without creating an account.
  </p>
  <p>
    The included tools run locally in the visitor's browser. Text entered into a
    tool is processed on the device, not sent to a custom application server.
    Some tools may optionally save input in localStorage so a draft remains
    available after a page refresh.
  </p>
  <p>
    Use this page to introduce your brand, explain who maintains the site, and
    describe the kinds of tools you publish.
  </p>
</ArticleLayout>
